Author: Itotsight
Text: Yeah. It ain't pretty and it doesn't do any good to our mental healt when eating from garbage, chewed food etc. because it fucks you up from inside when you do something like that too. It's worse than humiliating.

Author: elite-alien
Text: This is so real. I wish people saw this side of EDs more than the "skinny, pretty ballerina" type. It's not glamorous. I've also eaten chewed food, garbage food, food I out cigarettes out on..
